(22485, 'Meglucon 850mg 30 f.c.tab.', 'ميجلوكون 850مجم 30 قرص', '', '8', 'Metformin hydrochloride', 'October pharma > hexal ag germany', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Anti-diabetic.sensitizers.biguanide', '850mg', '**Metformin immediate-release formulations**
